reviewText: Pleasant film that makes me smile......Elvis was a great actor as can be seen in his better films such as King Creole, Flaming Star, Wild in the Country, Kid Galahad, etc.  This one is still good but, I can see why he got tired of the 'formula'......same story, different location. His talent was wasted because of a greedy manager and it damaged Elvis' spirit.  Such a beautiful human being who would still be with us had he taken complete charge of his own destiny.  No one else made such an impact in just 23 years.
ONE OF MY FAVORITE ELVIS MOVIES
